  "title": "Project Assistant Manager | Strong MEP Exp. (Piping, HVAC, Drainage System) | Industry Kitchen",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a leading player in <strong>Kitchen Appliance Industry.</strong> They are looking for a <strong>Project Assistant Manager</strong> to join their Team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the <strong>East area</strong> – easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Plan, schedule, and manage assigned projects from initiation to completion.</li><li>Allocate resources effectively, including manpower, materials, and equipment, to meet project requirements.</li><li>Monitor project costs, timelines, and progress to ensure delivery within budget and schedule.</li><li>Support the superior in project planning, cost management, time management, quality management, contract administration, and safety management.</li><li>Oversee daily project operations, addressing both strategic planning and detailed execution requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in civil/mechanical/electronic engineering or equivalent</li><li>Understand in MEP building systems (Mechanical, Electrical, and Plumbing)</li><li><strong>Must possess own vehicle </strong></li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R25157233</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Loh Pooi Keng</li></ul>",
